Les Paul Studio Deluxe Silverburst Limited Edition 2018 Item Description

This is a New Old Stock Les Paul Studio Deluxe model from Gibson USA. It's a 2018 guitar that's never been owned or played! The features include a slick Silverburst finish over a maple top, with a lightweight Ultra Modern weight-relieved mahogany body, and Burstbucker humbuckers. The electronics allow you to get coil split, coil select and pure boost options via four push-pulls, and the chrome Grover tuners ensure you'll stay in tune!

Includes: Hardshell Case

Product Specs and Features

Solidbody Electric Guitar

Silverburst Finish

Maple Top and Weight Relieved Mahogany Body

Slim Taper Profile Mahogany Neck

Rosewood Fingerboard

Trapezoid Inlays

24 3/4" Scale Length

12" Radius

1.695" Neck Width at Nut

22 Frets

Burstbucker 1 and 2 Humbucker Pickups

Individual Volume Controls and Tone Controls with Pure Boost, Coil Split and Coil Select Electronics

Three-Way Selector Switch

Tune-o-Matic Bridge Bridge

Chrome Hardware

8 lbs, 10 oz.
